content:
Hi all, I‘d like to see the Call Her Daddy episode full video. I can finde video snippets everywhere, and the audio podcast. But not video. 

Omg. “Some of us are not aspiring to be humble.” Best line evar. 

I am so conflicted because I think Harris is the best candidate in modern times who represents my POV and then I read news about Blinken approving bombs on humanitarian aid (both paid for by our tax dollars). 

Just going to trust the process for now.

Hi KT -- I've not been able to find the full video either. Here are two powerful clips of about 7-10 minutes   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_KCRsjPCiCI&t=1s  https://www.realclearpolitics.com/video/2024/10/06/full_interview_kamala_harris_on_call_her_daddy_podcast.html  The youtube one was posted in the news channel last night
I found a weird youtube that has the whole video, but they have replaced the background with weird graphics, and I wouldn't want to send it around. Do you want the link?
It is available through Spotify, though you may need an account to view the video.

Thanks for the reminder to watch it. It was a great interview with some hard questions. My favorite quote from Kamala: “Some people think the measure of the strength of a leader is based on who they beat down, but the true measure of the strength of a leader is based on who they lift up.” KAMALA FOR THE WIN!!!
Yes I believe she has a Spotify contract so full episodes are only there. https://open.spotify.com/episode/4B9WOUCWY8qY0f9MMjOSXa?si=91e53b46fe874c99
